软件包 gui

Contains the classes of Graphical User Interface.

请参见：
          描述

类摘要
DTNSimGUI Graphical User Interface for simulator
EventLogControl Class capsulates the references to the controls one can add to the EventLogControlPanel
EventLogControlPanel Control panel for event log
EventLogPanel Event log panel where log entries are displayed.
GUIControls GUI's control panel
InfoPanel Information panel that shows data of selected messages and nodes.
MainWindow Main window for the program.
NodeChooser Node chooser panel
RoutingInfoWindow A window for displaying routing information
SimMenuBar Menu bar of the simulator GUI
